summary:
I continuously seek to develop my personal skills, educational background, and achieve success in professional life. After nearly two years in the Marketing and PR sector, I found myself to be more data-oriented and interested in Data Science. This motivated me to study MS Data Science at University of Warsaw.
At the moment, I am developing my programming and data science skills in various programming languages, but mainly, R, Python and SQL.
